body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello! Welcome to SpeedyCars Customer Support. My name is Jerry Johnson. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Diane. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hi Jerry! I'm feeling happy today. I'm looking to purchase a car.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: That's great to hear, Diane! Can you provide me with your phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's five five five, eight one two, nine zero four six.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Diane. And for security purposes, could you also provide me with the last four digits of your social security number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, it's two three four five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing the information, Diane. We'll help you find the perfect car. Is there anything specific you're looking for?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm interested in a compact SUV with good fuel efficiency.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great choice! Thank you for sharing your preferences. We'll get started on finding the right vehicle for you. Thank you for your time, Diane. Have a wonderful day ahead.
